        <item>
            <title>【MWC2025】小米发布 15 Ultra 国际版，支援 iPhone 互传相 / 片 + 同场发布 15 + 开售详情公布</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/mi15ultra-intl-version-launched-hk-price-revealed/review-2/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mi15ultra-intl-version-launched-hk-price-revealed</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/03/mi15ultra-intl-version-launched-hk-price-revealed/review-2/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 03 Mar 2025 04:02:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[15]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[15 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[leica]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[mi]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米 15]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米 15 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294971</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米在香港时间中午 12 时就在西班牙巴塞隆那的 MWC 大会前夕，发布了新一代的真。旗舰拍摄手机 15 Ultra 的国际版，亦同场宣布会推出国际版的小米 15，现场亦公布了香港的开售详情，想知更多就要浏览 Edward 的现场报导了。</p><h2>15 Ultra 国行发布一星期旋即推国际版</h2><p>首先最引人注目的，肯定是小米在推出 15 Ultra 国行版本数天后，旋即推出该机的国际版。它在外形上继承了一部分上代小米 14 Ultra 的特点，机背黑、白色采用了航天级玻璃纤维作机背，而最特别的黑银色更结合了航天级玻璃纤维及 PU 皮革作机揹物料，十分有 LEICA 相机的设计风格。另外，机身亦采用了升级版的 Xiaomi Guardian 架构，耐跌表现比以往采用 Xiaomi Shield Glass 2.0 的机款提升了 16 倍，而框架亦采用了高强度电脑加工制的铝金属物料，令机身保持轻巧之余亦不失高耐用度。镜头亦同样采用了 Corning Gorilla Glass 7i 强化玻璃保护，有效提升抗摔防刮等效果。加上机身支援 IP68 防水防尘功能，令使用上亦更安心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295002" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09979-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09979-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09979.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这就是小米最新推出的 15 Ultra 国际版，大家可以见到从正面看，与上代分别不算很大。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294999" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09952-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09952-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09952.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机背采用了航天级玻璃纤维作机背，微磨砂的表面既硬净亦颇有手感。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295081" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155821-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155821-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155821.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于白色机就在机背加入了曲线花纹，十分优雅漂亮。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295082" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155709-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155709-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155709.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295083" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155723-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155723-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250302_155723.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不过笔者觉得最有型的依然是这款黑银两色版本，设计上更像一部怀旧 LEICA 相机，使用时更有感觉。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295000" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09960-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09960-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09960.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲框架采用了高强度电脑加工制的铝金属物料，令机身保持轻巧之余亦不失高耐用度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295001" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09965-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09965-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09965.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身亦采用了升级版的 Xiaomi Guardian 架构，耐跌表现比以往采用 Xiaomi Shield Glass 2.0 的机款提升了 16 倍。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295003" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09982-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09982-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09982.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294996" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09984-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09984-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09984.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲机身不算厚及阔，单手握机操控手感算不错。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294998" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09990-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09990-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09990.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294997" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09988-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09988-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09988.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲重量方面，小米 15 Ultra 为 229.3g，不算很重。</p><h2>「双大底」相机远近拍摄均佳</h2><p>而重点的相机方面，今代采用了「大三元」式全焦段镜头配置，主镜除了延续采用 LEICA Summilux 镜头组及 8P 非球面高透光镜片外，四个主镜亦覆盖了由 14mm 超广角到 200mm 超长焦全焦段，令用家拍摄时更具弹性。当中除了 5,000 万像素主摄依然采用了「超大底」1 吋感光元件外，超长焦的像素亦提升至 2 亿像素，感光元件尺寸亦达到 1/1.4 吋，这种「双大底」配置令用家无论是使用主摄镜还是超长焦镜拍摄，远近的成像质素，尤其是低光、夜摄场景中也有明显提升。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295014" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09956-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09956-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09956.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次小米 15 Ultra 依然采用 LEICA Summilux 镜头组及 8P 非球面高透光镜片架构，设有 4 个镜头，分别是均是 5,000 万像素的主摄镜、超广角镜、浮动长焦镜、以及 2 亿像素的潜望长焦镜。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295015" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09959-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09959-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc09959.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次的主相机最特别的地方，就是除了主摄镜依然采用 1 吋感光元件外，潜望长焦镜的感光元件亦达到 1/1.4 吋，这个「双大底」配置，理论上可令远近的成像质素，尤其是低光、夜摄场景中也有明显提升，不过亦因如此，主相机模组依然有一定厚度及面积。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295018" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-1-694x312.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="312" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-1-694x312.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295019" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-2-694x312.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="312" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-2-694x312.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲大家亦可见到只有超级长焦镜可以在超高清模式拍到 2 亿像素相片，其他镜头就只能拍到最高 5,000 万像素。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295016" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502241-694x312.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="312" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502241-694x312.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502241.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲小米 15 Ultra 介面上有少许改动，副目录改为用手指一滑拉出，比以往要滑到最尽头的目录再选择更顺手。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113759-670x580.jpg" alt="" width="670" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113759-670x580.jpg 670w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113759-scaled.jpg 1040w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 670px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295036" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113802-670x580.jpg" alt="" width="670" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113802-670x580.jpg 670w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113802-scaled.jpg 1040w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 670px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295037" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113807-670x580.jpg" alt="" width="670" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113807-670x580.jpg 670w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113807-scaled.jpg 1040w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 670px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295038" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113809-668x580.jpg" alt="" width="668" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113809-668x580.jpg 668w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_113809-scaled.jpg 1036w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 668px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这就是在日间以 4 个镜头：超广角（第一张）、主摄（第二张）、浮动长焦（第三张）及潜望长焦（第四张）镜拍摄的效果，大家可以见到每个镜头成像都十分不错，颜色还原度高之余亦十分清晰，即使暗位亦能看到一定程度的细节，表现值得一赞。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295039" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_120457-391x580.jpg" alt="" width="391" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_120457-391x580.jpg 391w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_120457-607x900.jpg 607w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_120457-scaled.jpg 608w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 391px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲当中潜望长焦镜可以有效压缩取景，令相片主题更集中。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1295040 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_145122-391x580.jpg" alt="" width="391" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_145122-391x580.jpg 391w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_145122-607x900.jpg 607w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_145122-scaled.jpg 608w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 391px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1295041 alignnone" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_150642-391x580.jpg" alt="" width="391" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_150642-391x580.jpg 391w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_150642-607x900.jpg 607w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_150642-scaled.jpg 608w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 391px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而使用潜望长焦镜拍摄人像相片，效果亦十分吸引。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295017" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-694x312.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="312" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260-694x312.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/screenshot_202502260.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲此外，小米 15 Ultra 的远摄亦加入了 AI 功能提升清晰度，只要点按下方的 AI 按键就可以了。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295042" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144745-668x580.jpg" alt="" width="668" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144745-668x580.jpg 668w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144745-scaled.jpg 1036w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 668px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144749-668x580.jpg" alt="" width="668" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144749-668x580.jpg 668w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/img_20250301_144749-scaled.jpg 1036w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 668px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这两张就是在圣家堂室内，在以潜望长焦镜及 120x 2791mm 数码变焦拍摄，分别没有开启 AI 清晰化（第一张）及开启了 AI 清晰化（第二张）两者的效果，大家很明显见到 AI 补图的相片，真的清晰很多，而且与真实情况近乎完全相同，可见 AI 表现十分不错。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1295009" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00839-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00839-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/dsc00839.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外今次小米的街拍模式，亦十分方便大家快速拍摄相片，如果配合手柄的话会更好玩，下文会再详述。</p><br /><b>
